Package: panelecon
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Panel Econometric Methods
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: person("Muhammad Abdullah", "Alkhalaf", email = "muhammedalkhalaf@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-2677-9246"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for panel data econometrics including
    pre-testing for unit roots (Hsiao homogeneity tests, Swamy parameter
    heterogeneity test), cross-sectional dependence testing in quantile
    regressions, panel Granger causality tests (Fourier Toda-Yamamoto and
    quantile), group-mean and pooled fully modified OLS estimation, quantile
    regression slope homogeneity tests, panel quantile unit root tests with
    common shocks and structural breaks, fixed effects vector decomposition
    and filtered estimators, and missing data detection and imputation for
    panel data.
